OL,5, Locking down small areas during the    
OL,6, autumn of 2020 was a "failed           
OL,7, experiment", First Minister Mark       
OL,8, Drakeford has told the Covid inquiry.  
OL,10,FSome council areas and towns like      
OL,11,FLlanelli and Bangor were subject to    
OL,12,Frestrictions as officials struggled to 
OL,13,Fcope with rising case numbers.         
OL,15,FA senior Welsh advisor said that in    
OL,16,Fhindsight "perhaps they weren't the    
OL,17,Fbest idea".                            
OL,19,FRob Orford told the inquiry that       
OL,20,Flockdowns made it more "complicated".  
